reset_min_transition(25.10)                        reset_min_transition(25.10)

Name
       reset_min_transition

Syntax
       reset_min_transition

       <object_list>

       Resets   minimum   slew   (transition)   limit   specified  (using  the
       set_min_transition command) on the objects  in  the  object  list.  The
       valid objects in the object list are primary ports, clocks, and current
       design.

Parameters
       <object_list>
              Specifies the list of ports, modules, and/or clock waveforms for
              which assertions are reset.

Related Information
              * set_min_transition

